<CATEGORY> international </CATEGORY>
<HEADLINE>  Moscoso Wins Panama Presidency </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	PANAMA CITY, Panama (AP) -- Mireya Moscoso took her place in  
Panamanian history today, winning election as the nation's first 
woman president and tasting sweet revenge as she beat the son of 
the man who overthrew her husband years ago. 
</P>
<P>
	Moscoso, the widow of an ousted president, will also get to  
