<HEADLINE>  Star Wars: May the Toys Be With You </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- After months of waiting and anticipation,  
anxious ``Star Wars'' fans braved the dead of night to get first 
dibs on the most-hyped line of movie-themed merchandise in history. 
</P>
