<HEADLINE> New WNBA Teams Get More Players </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- The WNBA allocated Katie Smith to the Minnesota  
Lynx and Shannon Johnson to the Orlando Miracle Monday as second 
players assigned to each expansion team. 
</P>
<P>
	Earlier, Nykesha Sales was given to Orlando and Kristin Folkl to  
