<HEADLINE>  Voting Begins in Nepalese Elections </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	KATMANDU, Nepal (AP) -- Wearing caps and capes in party colors,  
Nepalese waited in long lines today to elect a new parliament while 
security forces stood guard against more attacks by Maoist 
guerrillas. 
