<HEADLINE>  'Nightingales' Nominated for Tony </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Arthur Miller, the nation's most distinguished  
living playwright, and two other titans of the American theater -- 
the late Tennessee Williams and Eugene O'Neill -- dominated 
